text: Harmeet Singh Kalka (born 23 August 1968 in New Delhi, India) is an Indian politician and member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. Kalka was a member of the Delhi Legislative Assembly from the Kalkaji constituency of the South Delhi.My NetaMember's Particulars == References == Category:People from New Delhi Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians from Delhi Category:Members of the Delhi Legislative Assembly Category:Living people Category:21st-century Indian politicians Category:1968 births
